  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are 13.1 and 26.2 stickers and what do they mean?",
  "response": "The numbers **13.1** and **26.2** are commonly associated with running distances, specifically related to marathon events. Here's what they represent and how stickers featuring these numbers are typically used:\n\n### **13.1 Miles \u2013 Half Marathon**\n- **Distance:** 13.1 miles (21.097 kilometers)\n- **Description:** A half marathon is exactly half the distance of a full marathon. It's a popular race distance that attracts both novice and experienced runners.\n- **Stickers Usage:** Runners often receive or purchase stickers commemorating their achievement of completing a half marathon. These stickers can feature \"13.1\" prominently and are commonly displayed on items like water bottles, running gear, cars, or personal items to celebrate the accomplishment.\n\n### **26.2 Miles \u2013 Full Marathon**\n- **Distance:** 26.2 miles (42.195 kilometers)\n- **Description:** A full marathon is a long-distance running event with an official distance of 26.2 miles. It's one of the most challenging and prestigious events in the running community.\n- **Stickers Usage:** Similar to half marathons, participants in full marathons may receive or buy stickers marked with \"26.2\" to signify the feat of completing a marathon. These stickers serve as badges of honor and can be displayed on various personal belongings as a mark of endurance and dedication.\n\n### **Purpose of the Stickers**\n- **Commemoration:** They serve as mementos to remember the race and the effort put into training and completing it.\n- **Recognition:** Stickers help others recognize the runner's achievement, often sparking conversations or admiration.\n- **Motivation:** Displaying these stickers can inspire continued participation in running events or other personal goals.\n\n### **Design and Variations**\n- **Customization:** Many race organizers offer customized stickers with the race's logo, date, and location alongside the distance (13.1 or 26.2).\n- **Creative Designs:** Beyond the numerical representation, some stickers feature artistic designs, slogans, or symbols related to running and fitness.\n\n### **Conclusion**\nIf you come across \"13.1\" and \"26.2\" stickers, they're most likely commemorating participation or completion of a half marathon and full marathon, respectively. These stickers are popular among runners as symbols of their achievements and milestones in the sport of long-distance running.",
